## How This Wiki Is Organized

Every scanned repository has its own full wiki tree with:

- **Overview** — what the repo does, its stack, entry points
- **Architecture** — layers, Mermaid diagrams, dependency graph
- **Onboarding** — a suggested reading path for new contributors
- **Modules** — one page per architectural layer
- **Flows** — one page per tour step
- **Diagrams** — architecture + dependency Mermaid sources

Use the **"Repos" dropdown** in the top navbar to switch between them.

## Primary Repository

The **primary repo** is highlighted with ⭐ above. It is the target of the current
tGD project — additional repos are scanned as **context** to help you navigate
cross-repo dependencies.

